[0.089, "o", "daily-bcp reads Daily Office readings, collects, common prayers, and devotions.\r\n\r\nTry:\r\n  bcp readings\r\n  bcp readings morning\r\n  bcp readings --date tomorrow\r\n  bcp collects sat\r\n  bcp history\r\n  bcp history --verbose\r\n\r\nRun `bcp --help` for all options.\r\n"]
